    "Answer sources": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Fuentes de la respuesta"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Any /chat/completions endpoint works: OpenAI, OpenRouter, Groq, or a local Ollama/LM Studio server (http://localhost:11434/v1 — there, nothing leaves your device). When the switch is on, Companion sends ONLY the detected question text — never audio or the rest of the meeting — and each card says who answered. If the provider fails, the answer falls back to the local model.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sirve cualquier endpoint /chat/completions: OpenAI, OpenRouter, Groq, o un Ollama/LM Studio local (http://localhost:11434/v1 — ahí nada sale de tu equipo). Con el interruptor activo, Companion envía SOLO el texto de la pregunta detectada — nunca audio ni el resto de la reunión — y cada tarjeta dice quién respondió. Si el proveedor falla, la respuesta cae al modelo local."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Apple (on-device)": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple (en el dispositivo)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Apple Intelligence requires macOS 26 — choose Ollama in Settings.": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple Intelligence requiere macOS 26 — elige Ollama en Ajustes."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Apple uses Foundation Models (macOS 26 + Apple Intelligence). Ollama runs a 100% local model on your Mac — ideal if you do not have Apple Intelligence. Either way, nothing leaves the device. (The LIVE summary during recording always uses Apple.)": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple usa Foundation Models (macOS 26 + Apple Intelligence). Ollama corre un modelo 100% local en tu Mac — ideal si no tienes Apple Intelligence. Con cualquiera, nada sale del equipo. (El resumen EN VIVO durante la grabación siempre usa Apple.)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Apple uses Foundation Models (macOS 26 + Apple Intelligence). Ollama runs a 100% local model on your Mac. Built-in runs an embedded 4B model (one 3 GB verified download) with zero installs. Either way, nothing leaves the device. (The LIVE summary during recording always uses Apple.)": {
      "localizations": {
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple usa Foundation Models (macOS 26 + Apple Intelligence). Ollama corre un modelo 100% local en tu Mac. Integrado corre un modelo 4B embebido (una descarga verificada de 3 GB) sin instalar nada. En todos los casos, nada sale del equipo. (El resumen EN VIVO durante la grabación siempre usa Apple.)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
